# Mobile architecture

## Layers (`mobile/lib/`)

| Layer | Path |
|-------|------|
| App | `app/router.dart`, `app/di/injection.dart` |
| Core | `core/network/`, `core/design_system/`, `core/storage/` |
| Domain | `domain/entities/`, `domain/repositories/`, `domain/usecases/` |
| Data | `data/datasources/`, `data/repositories/*_impl.dart` |
| Presentation | `presentation/<feature>/` |

## Patterns

- **Routing:** `go_router` in `app/router.dart` — add routes + redirect guards there.
- **DI:** GetIt `sl` — register in `injection.dart`.
- **State:** `Cubit` for onboarding only; other screens call repos/use cases directly.
- **API:** `PayspinApiClient` — base URL from `--dart-define=API_URL`.

## New screen

1. Page in `presentation/<feature>/`
2. Route in `router.dart`
3. Repo method if new API endpoint
4. Register deps in `injection.dart`

## UI design

See `.cursor/rules/payspin-design.mdc` — dark prototype, `PayspinTheme`, gradient CTAs.

## Run

```bash
cd mobile
flutter run --dart-define=API_URL=http://localhost:3001/v1
```

Driver tests: `lib/main_driver.dart` (extension before `ensureInitialized`).
